{"tid":1594564,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"智取黑警","createTime":"2019-09-25T15:30:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T15:36:38.000Z","uid":296447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"37daa619366a336dc8585eb39a3cd19c4552e29a","tid":1594564,"uid":296447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:30:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑警犯法事多蘿蘿。無謂送頭，集中查違警例的行為，如<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n1. 借大耳隆的狗，因違警例第6章6-01<br />\n2. 做未得上頭同意的外間工作，違第6章6-26<br />\n3. 與已知的罪犯或三合會會員來往，違6章6-01<br />\n4. 收數睇場等犯罪行為，違貪污條例和其他章則<br />\n</span><br />\n捉得幾多就幾多。</span>"},{"pid":"1550570a1265fac545b718e01ab4cb6bcc957f22","tid":1594564,"uid":296447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:32:23.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"b49de544e555eb4c2e78ce3c70db3e5f9c157d26","tid":1594564,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:34:54.000Z","msg":"內裏互相包庇<br />\n你仲信現今制度制裁到黑警<br />\n未免太天真"},{"pid":"24c76a6db83489377023feb9edb497f8d8b15e87","tid":1594564,"uid":70127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:36:38.000Z","msg":"太天真"}]}